{"tid":232707,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【餘波未了】貨幣操縱累輸錢！傳投資者擬向滙控等興訴訟","createTime":"2017-05-07T03:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T12:24:21.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7d85878844e185115dfe4a64a0070dd9aae502","tid":232707,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/112135_52fd2b2a092d29b5c9833548e02d87f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F112135_52fd2b2a092d29b5c9833548e02d87f3.jpg&h=53217250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，部份全球最大的投資者正與美國律師事務所商討，將針對部份銀行開展新一輪的訴訟，指有關銀行操控外匯市場交易，令基金蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士透露，今次興起訟訴的投資者包括貝萊德、太平洋投資管理以及對沖基金BlueCrest，至於針對銀行包括巴克萊、花旗、滙控、摩通、蘇皇以及瑞銀。有關律師行計劃分別於倫敦及紐約入稟，希望可吸引更多投資者加入行動。<br />\n<br />\n此外，今次興起訴訟的幾位投資者同時亦會研究，會否退出向滙控、巴克萊、蘇皇以及高盛貨幣操縱的集體訴訟。因退出將有利於規模較大的投資者尋求更佳的和解方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56657676&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56657676%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=6fc6f5c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56657676%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170506&h=d5bfd526\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56657676&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170506</a>"},{"pid":"77501335570cf93b4db3d47ea87e1ceae5397ce8","tid":232707,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"唔怪得有玩fx巴打話九成散戶輸錢"},{"pid":"c745f462a30772468bc9105669a048d9c3e48ff7","tid":232707,"uid":98381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:24:21.000